object.customQuery:
SELECT attachment.SystemId, attachment.ParentId, attachment.CMMContainer, attachment.Id, attachment.UpdateCount, attachment.UpdateUser, attachment.UpdateTimestamp, attachment.IdRef, attachment.TemplateId, attachment.Description, attachment.Filename, attachment.OriginalFilename, attachment.Memo, attachment.Status, attachment.AddDt, attachment.AddTm, attachment.AddUser, attachment.UpdateDt, attachment.UpdateTm, attachment.HasAnnotationsInd, attachment.TransactionNumber, attachment.SourceRef, attachment.SourceContainerName, attachment.RowId 
FROM
 attachment where attachment.CMMContainer in ('Claim', 'Policy')
and systemid in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and cmmcontainer in ('Claim', 'Policy'))
